data.description:
Welcome to 5409 Holster Dr, the perfect home for you and your family. With four bedrooms and two bathrooms, you'll have plenty of space to live and grow. Enjoy the convenience of the tile flooring and the energy-efficiency of the ceiling fans throughout the home. The garage door opener adds convenience and ease of access to the property.

This property is located in a prime spot, just minutes away from Fort Cavazos and Lions Park. You'll enjoy the convenience of being close to a variety of amenities, while still enjoying the privacy and comfort of your own home.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours. Schedule a viewing today and discover the potential of 5409 Holster Dr.
